br />\n但三個都係goat之一，計高峰好難比較高低"},{"pid":"61e6eaf1a86ded983e44b2de9d16e4fe4f0b377e","tid":768052,"uid":13090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:37:18.000Z","msg":"講最top狀態定講今年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031da46a3470b45a107ab485e128561f9d681d5e","tid":768052,"uid":155902,"like":1,"dislike":37,"score":-36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:38:51.000Z","msg":"祖高域吊打晒另外兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54e0277654282a6563c4bda80a03b4b3b83da19","tid":768052,"uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":33,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:40:06.000Z","msg":"祖 &gt; 費 &gt; 拿"},{"pid":"200ad142d39d1b06eb6798b8609aefea162fa00f","tid":768052,"uid":18912,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"aec0fb7b86d008a4d48a7394dbfef382e7c3e7c4","tid":768052,"uid":19858,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ae8b1064df4841fcf883bf74235b0d2fddbeff6e","tid":768052,"uid":555,"like":109,"dislike":2,"score":107,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:32:39.000Z","msg":"你排咗啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪就係順序"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:40:25.000Z","msg":"計grand slam就一定係呢個順序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nNadal雖然career golden slam<br />\n不過四大入面太偏French open<br />\n雖然對賽lead federer都唔覺可以排得高過federer🤔"},{"pid":"f757774ee288d080deb197821bea05d4f74b2aff","tid":768052,"uid":18912,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7478d6495c1537ffb93cff638578e458256f2df8","tid":768052,"uid":555,"like":9,"dislike":49,"score":-40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:34:43.000Z","msg":"巔峰djo實力應該3人之中最強"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:42:38.000Z","msg":"個人一直好鐘意有djo既出現去打破兩強局面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbf655d074b8b6646d88f10a9214a3130c4b5d8","tid":768052,"uid":19858,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:43:06.000Z","msg":"總之聽親網球比賽<br />\n有Federer個名就多數係晉級、入決賽、捧盃<br />\n個穩定性非常高<br />\n當然拿度都係較多<br />\n祖高域印象中某三幾年處於屈另外2位機既狀態<br />\n但好似無法維持"},{"pid":"d694583212635d7466a16dddb75df3b46de18050","tid":768052,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61e6eaf1a86ded983e44b2de9d16e4fe4f0b377e","tid":768052,"uid":13090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:37:18.000Z","msg":"講最top狀態定講今年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:46:58.000Z","msg":"好多chings已經講左top狀態既rank<br />\n可以講下今年👌"},{"pid":"0846d7275f61e4ea8110a2cd55caf25d30a68b7f","tid":768052,"uid":70951,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:48:23.000Z","msg":"小明career gold slam....應該好難唔係佢"},{"pid":"f00e72cbf630683f473bb593e60b32dd2c38ba4a","tid":768052,"uid":155137,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:48:31.000Z","msg":"費係傳奇唔洗講<br />\n拿係泥地傳奇<br />\n祖係好波 但係好似無稱得上為傳奇戰績（雖然有唔少gs）"},{"pid":"04f55844b3f567c9cf7b3671492fe2357a6b62ee","tid":768052,"uid":18912,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"f00e72cbf630683f473bb593e60b32dd2c38ba4a","tid":768052,"uid":155137,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:48:31.000Z","msg":"費係傳奇唔洗講<br />\n拿係泥地傳奇<br />\n祖係好波 但係好似無稱得上為傳奇戰績（雖然有唔少gs）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:54:56.000Z","msg":"只係因為祖同期有費同拿兩個je<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祖既gs對比歷史名將已經一啲都唔失禮<br />\n更何況佢係打破兩強果個<br />\n好似如果美斯朗之外有一個公認可以挑佢兩個機既冠軍選手出現<br />\n都唔會唔係傳奇吧"},{"pid":"61f6d8a7c0dc98b87dbc2940a30f7a2a4228e4d5","tid":768052,"uid":31423,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:33:31.000Z","msg":"費 祖 拿"},{"pid":"ef4ead578098988cd18925f3af99ad3a2f828fa6","tid":768052,"uid":55193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:36:54.000Z","msg":"其實好難直接比較 費prime時期好撚無敵 但正式同輩對手都接近全收皮 得拿度後起之秀挑戰佢 到拿度prime 費又開始頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拿度就傷患影響冇長時期穩定既prime 到祖打起左 佢prime果時前2個又係谷底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果陣時得梅利短暫打起左但威脅又唔算好大"},{"pid":"474c873b0765903e02ac0e9b2b496a1e1593dbad","tid":768052,"uid":29675,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:37:07.000Z","msg":"梅利表示:我呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea13665b8d969558e4814da51a67cb64adfb081","tid":768052,"uid":18912,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"474c873b0765903e02ac0e9b2b496a1e1593dbad","tid":768052,"uid":29675,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:37:07.000Z","msg":"梅利表示:我呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:41:39.000Z","msg":"Prize money\t<br />\nUS$ 60,863,600<br />\n<br />\n 4th all-time leader in earnings"},{"pid":"95e14ec9dc110c82778544978d445ab74ba7aa36","tid":768052,"uid":89820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"474c873b0765903e02ac0e9b2b496a1e1593dbad","tid":768052,"uid":29675,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:37:07.000Z","msg":"梅利表示:我呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:46:35.000Z","msg":"依個就差半班了"},{"pid":"89008eb099c2b0c8ac65d8b232f3ac2696e4fd5b","tid":768052,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"95e14ec9dc110c82778544978d445ab74ba7aa36","tid":768052,"uid":89820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"474c873b0765903e02ac0e9b2b496a1e1593dbad","tid":768052,"uid":29675,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:37:07.000Z","msg":"梅利表示:我呢<img src=\"/asse